@startuml
title StudentTuition Class Diagram - School Management System

hide circle

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam ClassBorderColor #334155
skinparam ClassBackgroundColor white
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FEF9C3
skinparam NoteBorderColor #A16207

class StudentTuition {
  -id: bigint
  -student_id: bigint
  -course_id: bigint
  -course_price: integer

  --
  +student(): BelongsTo
  +course(): BelongsTo
}

note right of StudentTuition
StudentTuition stores the course
price assigned to a student at
the time of enrollment.

It links the student to the course
used for tuition calculation.
end note

@enduml